text: Advincula is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Arcenio James Advincula (born 1938), American martial artist *Jose Advincula (born 1952), Filipino Roman Catholic archbishop *Luis Advíncula (born 1990), Peruvian footballer *Paul Advincula (born 1964), Filipino basketball coach ==See also== *23017 Advincula, a main-belt asteroid
